faq_subtitle: Find answers to common questions about DreamImg AI.
faq1_answer: DreamImg AI is the world's first completely free, unlimited AI image generator, powered by the Seedream3.0 model. It allows you to create high-quality images from text descriptions without any registration or usage limits.
faq2_question: Is it really free to use?
faq2_answer: Yes, DreamImg AI is 100% free with no hidden costs. You can generate an unlimited number of images without any subscriptions or fees.
faq3_question: What makes DreamImg AI different from other image generators?
faq3_answer: DreamImg AI is the only platform that offers unlimited free access to the powerful Seedream3.0 model. We provide exceptional image quality, fast generation speeds, and complete privacy, all without any cost or registration requirements.
faq4_question: Do I need an account to use the service?
faq4_answer: No, you can start creating images right away. We do not require any registration or personal information.
faq5_question: What kind of images can I create?
faq5_answer: You can create a wide variety of images, including photorealistic scenes, artistic illustrations, digital art, anime-style images, and more. The Seedream3.0 model excels at understanding complex prompts and generating diverse visual styles.
faq6_question: Are there any limitations on image generation?
faq6_answer: There are no limitations on the number of images you can generate. Feel free to explore your creativity without any restrictions.
